---
// Static terminal window — bilingual bio in monospace
---

<div class="terminal-window terminal-bio">
  <div class="terminal-window__bar">
    <span class="terminal-window__dot terminal-window__dot--red"></span>
    <span class="terminal-window__dot terminal-window__dot--amber"></span>
    <span class="terminal-window__dot terminal-window__dot--green"></span>
    <span class="terminal-window__title">fei-yueh@ur ~ %</span>
  </div>
  <div class="terminal-window__body">
    <div class="t-line">
      <span class="terminal-window__prompt">$ </span>
      <span class="terminal-window__output lang-en">whoami</span>
      <span class="terminal-window__output lang-zh">我是誰</span>
    </div>
    <div class="t-line t-val">
      <span class="lang-en-block">AI researcher · University of Rochester (ECE + Computational Linguistics)</span>
      <span class="lang-zh-block">AI 研究者・羅徹斯特大學（電機 + 計算語言學）</span>
    </div>

    <div class="t-line t-gap">
      <span class="terminal-window__prompt">$ </span>
      <span class="terminal-window__output lang-en">cat affiliations</span>
      <span class="terminal-window__output lang-zh">cat 研究單位</span>
    </div>
    <div class="t-line t-val">
      AIR Lab (Music AI) &nbsp;·&nbsp; Smule Inc &nbsp;·&nbsp; CCL Lab &nbsp;·&nbsp; Academia Sinica
    </div>

    <div class="t-line t-gap">
      <span class="terminal-window__prompt">$ </span>
      <span class="terminal-window__output lang-en">cat awards</span>
      <span class="terminal-window__output lang-zh">cat 獎項</span>
    </div>
    <div class="t-line t-val">
      <span class="lang-en-block">NeurIPS 2025 Best Paper · Taiwan Future Tech Award 2023</span>
      <span class="lang-zh-block">NeurIPS 2025 最佳論文獎 · 台灣未來科技獎 2023</span>
    </div>

    <div class="t-line t-gap">
      <span class="terminal-window__prompt">$ </span>
      <span class="terminal-window__output lang-en">cat interests</span>
      <span class="terminal-window__output lang-zh">cat 研究興趣</span>
    </div>
    <div class="t-line t-val">
      <span class="lang-en-block">Music generation · Vocal AI · LLMs · Speech · Spatial audio</span>
      <span class="lang-zh-block">音樂生成 · 歌聲 AI · 大型語言模型 · 語音 · 空間音訊</span>
    </div>

    <div class="t-line t-gap t-cursor">
      <span class="terminal-window__prompt">$ </span>
      <span class="cursor-blink">▋</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.terminal-bio {
  max-width: 600px;
}
.t-line {
  font-family: 'Redhat', monospace;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
}
.t-val {
  color: var(--color-text-code);
  padding-left: 1.2rem;
}
.t-gap {
  margin-top: 0.7rem;
}
.t-zh {
  font-family: 'GenYoMin2TW', serif;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.9;
}
.t-cursor {
  margin-top: 0.7rem;
}
.cursor-blink {
  color: var(--color-jade-light);
  animation: blink 1.1s step-end infinite;
}
@keyframes blink {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50%       { opacity: 0; }
}
</style>
